snippet.title: Aquanox 2 Revelation High Res Trailer
snippet.description:
A high res trailer for the little-known game Aquanox 2: Revelation. A great submarine game to make you fear the depths. 

Sadly, the series was canned along with its German developer, Massive Development. A waste of potential if there ever was one.

However, the series was recently revived by THQ Nordic with a new game called "Aquanox: The Deep Descent." Please check it out if you can.
